sequenceDiagram
    participant Views as wippy/views module
    participant API as /api/public/components/list
    participant WebHost as Web Host
    participant DOM as Page DOM
    participant CE as customElements

    WebHost->>API: GET /api/public/components/list
    Note over API: filters: announced == true
    API->>WebHost: [{tag_name, entry_point, url, auto_register}]
    loop for each auto_register component
        WebHost->>DOM: inject &lt;script type="module" src="entry_point?declare-tag=tag_name"&gt;
        DOM->>CE: define(import.meta.url, ElementClass)
        CE->>CE: customElements.define(tag_name, ElementClass)
    end
    Note over DOM: Components now available<br/>as custom HTML elements
